init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The rest of the day goes by in a blur.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Call the number listed, no matter what time of day or night."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The phone rings twice before someone answers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm sorry if we have startled you Barack, but this is how it works.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are given a dossier on the problems facing this alternate Earth, and told that you will be expected to act as necessary.
